bottom, and reuses the existing `--human` flag pattern for human-readable sizes.

---

## Critical Files

| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `crates/uv-cli/src/lib.rs` | CLI arg definition (`CacheCommand` enum, arg structs) |
| `crates/uv/src/lib.rs` | Top-level command dispatch |
| `crates/uv/src/commands/mod.rs` | Module declarations + re-exports |
| `crates/uv/src/commands/cache_size.rs` | Reference impl to copy patterns from |
| `crates/uv-cache/src/lib.rs` | `CacheBucket` enum, `Cache::bucket()` |
| `crates/uv-console/src/lib.rs` | `human_readable_bytes()` helper |
| `crates/uv-preview/src/lib.rs` | `PreviewFeature::CacheSize` (reused for stats) |
| `crates/uv-test/src/lib.rs` | `TestContext` – add helper + filter |
| `crates/uv/tests/it/main.rs` | Integration test module registry |
| `crates/uv/tests/it/cache_size.rs` | Reference test to copy patterns from |

---

